---
title: Honey-BBQ Pork Chops plus Garlicky Rice with Zucchini & Black Beans
description: Seasoned with honey and fiery, flavorful harissa powder, our sweet and spicy BBQ sauce elevates tender pork chops to new heights. The succulent chops are served with garlicky rice tossed with zucchini and black beans that soak up all the extra flavor. With a sprinkling of fresh scallions over top, this hearty meal is one you’ll keep coming back for!
